high_descs: Turn around to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick the white mug up from the shelf.
Go right and turn to the left to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the cup out.
Go to the right to stand in front of the coffee maker.
Put the cup under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed cup under a coffee pot.

high_descs: Turn around and face the fridge.
Grab the white mug from the fridge.
Walk to the stove to the right of the fridge and look at the microwave.
Warm the mug in the microwave, then take it out again.
Turn around, then turn left to reach the coffee machine.
Place the mug inside the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed mug in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn to your left then head to the fridge
Open the fridge and get the mug beside the cabbage inside the fridge then close the door
Turn to your right, move forward and face the microwave on your left
Open the microwave put in the mug in front of the apple, open the microwave then pick up the mug then close the door again
Turn around cross the room and head to the coffee maker
Put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the warm mug on the coffee maker
